{"tid":1592152,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦 我可以點做","createTime":"2019-09-24T13:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:39:52.000Z","uid":189308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"82ecc10dce016beef5590591be1cca988289e98e","tid":1592152,"uid":189308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"冇諗過第一次開po係因為唔開心到頂唔順<br />\n每日都不停怪責自己<br />\n係咁散發負能量 放負放到身邊既人都怕左你咁<br />\n日日返屋企就喊 喊到訓著<br />\n身邊嘅人問做咩瘦左禁多 食飯覺得我細食 其實我真係好冇胃口<br />\n做人好攰啊 <br />\n依排會諗就算依排有咩意外都好 我可以咩都唔洗再理<br />\n試過搵過網上輔導果啲好似冇咩用<br />\n始終人都係要靠自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經唔知可以點做 撐得好辛苦<br />\n我以為自己好堅強 但今次真係好難過"},{"pid":"385026fa5661cfc9852579dfcc0eae4898dab271","tid":1592152,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"97a62fcc0500d0250c874fb40430bc499dd6737c","tid":1592152,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"加油呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d87d040d9d4168d6ed9f338f707508a358d4d93","tid":1592152,"uid":141011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"之前同你有tg傾過計，你既情緒係以前已經係一直壓抑住，無去面對，就好似個氣球咁"},{"pid":"1e1a80e90495e57478e05c7c564b6a1c684711fe","tid":1592152,"uid":189308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d87d040d9d4168d6ed9f338f707508a358d4d93","tid":1592152,"uid":141011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"之前同你有tg傾過計，你既情緒係以前已經係一直壓抑住，無去面對，就好似個氣球咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"撐到禁耐 叻唔叻"},{"pid":"463d452c8df93574f92e34e